That might arrive in chunks like:

First chunk: <Buffer 7b 22 6e 61> // = {"na

Second chunk: <Buffer 6d 65 22 3a> // = me":

Third chunk: <Buffer 20 22 41 6c 69 63 65 22 7d> // = "Alice"}

You collect all chunks and then join them with:

